<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remove-vt">remove <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'muːv/    美 /rɪ'muːv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>移走；移开；搬走：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was too tired to remove the stone. 
他太累了，移不开那块石头。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>removed</strong> a notice <strong>from</strong> the door.
他揭掉了门上的告示。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>remove banana skins
剥香蕉皮</p><footer>2018 全国改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[正式用语] 摘掉；脱掉</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She removed the diamond ring to cook a meal.
为了做饭，她把钻戒摘了下来。</p><footer>2017 浙江改</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>消除；去掉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>remove sb’s fear / doubts 
消除某人的恐惧/疑虑</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>remove dark spots
袪黑头</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>把...免职；撤去：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>remove</strong> a man <strong>from</strong> office 
免除一个人的职务</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>removal /rɪ'muːvl/ n [C] &amp; [U]   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>When fat and salt <strong><em>_</em></strong><strong><em>_</em></strong>___ (remove) from food, the food tastes as if it is missing something.   （2017 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. are removed  </p></div>